Overview
Browser extension to help Power BI users export any dashboard in PDF without going to the Power BI portal. This also allows the users to export any page, even if it has Non-Certified Power BI Custom Visuals.

Our browser extension is designed to simplify the process of exporting reports from Power BI to PDF format. With our extension, you can easily save your reports as PDF files directly from the Power BI interface without the need for additional tools or complex procedures.

Key features:

Report export: Simply select the report you want to export and click the extension's icon.
Ease of use: Our extension integrates directly into the Power BI interface, providing simplicity and convenience.
With our extension, PDF export becomes fast and convenient, allowing you to easily save important data and share it with colleagues and stakeholders.
